          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-954-07E2-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">O</hi>N rainy days alone I dine</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-07E2-line-2" n="2">Upon a chick, and pint of wine.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-07E2-line-3" n="3">On rainy days I dine alone,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-07E2-line-4" n="4">And pick my chicken to the bone:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-07E2-line-5" n="5">But this my servants much enrages,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-07E2-line-6" n="6">No scraps remain to save board-wages.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-07E2-line-7" n="7">In weather fine I nothing spend,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-07E2-line-8" n="8">But often spunge upon a friend:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-07E2-line-9" n="9">Yet where he's not so rich as I;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-954-07E2-line-10" n="10">I pay my club, and so good b'y'────.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
